sequenceDiagram
  %% Authored stress fixture (Mermaid@11.12.2): nested rect + par/and branches with notes and activations.

  participant U as User
  participant S as Service
  participant W as Worker

  rect rgba(240,240,255,0.7)
    U->>S: Request
    activate S

    par processing
      S->>W: enqueue job
      activate W
      W-->>S: ready
      Note over S,W: job metadata<br/>line 2
      W-->>S: result
      deactivate W
    and telemetry
      S->>S: record metric
      Note right of S: local note
    end

    S-->>U: Response
    deactivate S
  end

